<li><a href="/wiki/List_of_World_Heritage_Sites_in_Nigeria" title="List of World Heritage Sites in Nigeria">World Heritage Sites</a></li></ul></div></div></td>
</tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content" style="padding:0.2em 0 0.6em;font-size:95%;">
