<li id="cite_note-Africanfolder.com-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Africanfolder.com_14-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://africanfolder.com/25-best-african-songs-of-all-time/">"25 Best African Songs Of All Time"</a>. Africanfolder.com<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">19 October</span> 2023</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=25+Best+African+Songs+Of+All+Time&amp;rft.pub=Africanfolder.com&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fafricanfolder.com%2F25-best-african-songs-of-all-time%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMusic+of+Nigeria" class="Z3988"></span></span>
